title: Can someone help me identify the fonts in this logo?
content:
Need help identifying the fonts in the ad, mostly the musketeers font

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150404114431im_/http:/typophile.com/files/25_4763.jpg)
author: flophouse85

comments.content:
SIOUX CITY: looks like some sort of [Futura](http://web.archive.org/web/20150404114431/http:/www.myfonts.com/search/futura) (Black) Inline... May be custom? Out-of-the-box: [Zamenhof](http://web.archive.org/web/20150404114431/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/castletype/zamenhof) Inline CT  
Musketeers: Schizotype [Gelato Script](http://web.archive.org/web/20150404114431/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/schizotype/gelato-script/regular/glyphs.html#glyphs/510383/81) using alternate / [M](http://web.archive.org/web/20150404114431/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/schizotype/gelato-script/regular/glyphs.html#glyphs/510383/81) and / [s](http://web.archive.org/web/20150404114431/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/schizotype/gelato-script/regular/glyphs.html#glyphs/510383/558)  
ONE TEAM: [Duke](http://web.archive.org/web/20150404114431/http:/losttype.com/font/?name=duke) Fill  
ONE GOAL: [Veneer YDS](http://web.archive.org/web/20150404114431/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/yellow-design/veneer)
